{"tid":1191221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【長文慎入】有冇人聽過『學習無助』？","createTime":"2019-06-07T19:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T10:55:36.000Z","uid":125597,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ff2218bb49fddafcfe2a29c60f0032d1488789fd","tid":1191221,"uid":125597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T19:57:17.000Z","msg":"學習無助，又稱習得無助，Learned Helplessness。<br />\n<br />\n當人對同一件事多次付出，但無法得到相對收穫，<br />\n甚至可能會受到懲罰，就會發現自己一直相信嘅因果關係並不存在。<br />\n<br />\n呢種情況下，人一直建立嘅信念會被擊潰，<br />\n行為再冇意義，因為無論係咩行為，都已經唔再可以改變到結果。<br />\n<br />\n呢一種『我嘅行為無法改變結果』嘅學習過程，<br />\n就被稱為『學習無助』。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲嘢關我春事？點解無啦啦要話我知？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為政府就係用緊人嘅呢種心理，<br />\n將你慢慢推緊入呢種無力感同埋絕望感入面啊！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n試諗下，雨傘其實絕對係香港政治運動史上輝煌嘅一筆，<br />\n但點解雨傘後極多香港人對政治嘅失望感同埋無力感會更大？<br />\n<br />\n就係因為執政者都好清楚人會有呢種心理狀態，<br />\n佢就係要不斷證明比你睇，無論係電視發牌、雨傘、DQ、送中&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我就係你點反我都唔理你啊！<br />\n仲要笑9你，拉幾條出啲嘅去坐監，殺雞儆猴，<br />\n話你知做咁多嘢都係冇用嘅，嘥9氣，<br />\n睇你下次仲會唔會出嚟反我啊垃圾！<br />\n<br />\n但請問香港人，點解你哋要參加政治運動？<br />\n真係純粹係想單一條例唔通過？<br />\n<br />\n抑或你哋有自己嘅一套價值想表達？<br />\n抑或你追求緊嘅，係一套你認可嘅公義？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，你所信守嘅價值，<br />\n就係組成所謂『港人精神』嘅一套價值。<br />\n<br />\n出嚟遊行，唔單只係想推翻一條惡法，<br />\n亦係為要捍衛自己嘅價值，堅守自己嘅原則。<br />\n<br />\n所以即使最後政府真係硬推，逃犯條例最後真係通過。<br />\n出嚟為自身價值同公義發聲嘅我哋，唔係空手而回。<br />\n<br />\n我亦拍咗一條關於『學習無助』嘅片，<br />\nYoutube search『黎天雅 學習無助』就會搵到，<br />\n想聽得清楚少少，而又唔介意本人樣唔靚、唔識製作嘅話亦可以睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n你可以話我係想賣廣告點點點，觀點亦係一種自由。<br />\n但我亦必須聲明，呢一刻我毋須負上會被圍剿嘅風險去拍一條敏感片搏出名。<br />\n<br />\n我亦會努力地尊重其他人所堅守嘅一套價值，即使有差異。<br />\n<br />\n因為當一個人對自己信守嘅價值有足夠信心，<br />\n就毋須強拉其他人入自己嘅陣營。<br />\n<br />\n和諧，唔係一百個人講同一句說話；<br />\n而係一百個人講一百句唔同說話之餘，而又互相尊重。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，六月九號見。"},{"pid":"6debf9f704b664ed85e84c1f085ffc3a4e0462ee","tid":1191221,"uid":389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T19:59:08.000Z","msg":"學習無助乜Term黎？<br />\n<br />\nLearned指經學習的<br />\n<br />\n香港一向叫習得性無助，或者習得無助"},{"pid":"1aa34b3b10247e1b7840f8bbf1e9d2c0befc0334","tid":1191221,"uid":125597,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6debf9f704b664ed85e84c1f085ffc3a4e0462ee","tid":1191221,"uid":389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T19:59:08.000Z","msg":"學習無助乜Term黎？<br />\n<br />\nLearned指經學習的<br />\n<br />\n香港一向叫習得性無助，或者習得無助"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T20:12:27.000Z","msg":"我知道係有唔同嘅譯名，<br />\n習得性失助、無助學習、習得無助，etc. <br />\n<br />\n但我讀書嘅時候聽嘅係學習無助，<br />\n所以要我揀譯名，我會選擇用學習無助。<br />\n<br />\n但譯名並非最重點，<br />\n眼見呢個理論同香港現況有關係，<br />\n故此我分享。<br />\n<br />\n我對呢個理論亦稱不上熟悉，<br />\n如果有人有更多補充，我極級歡迎。"},{"pid":"ad3b98ee67d4e6f60dea39a8c024fb5d7f636409","tid":1191221,"uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1aa34b3b10247e1b7840f8bbf1e9d2c0befc0334","tid":1191221,"uid":125597,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6debf9f704b664ed85e84c1f085ffc3a4e0462ee","tid":1191221,"uid":389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T19:59:08.000Z","msg":"學習無助乜Term黎？<br />\n<br />\nLearned指經學習的<br />\n<br />\n香港一向叫習得性無助，或者習得無助"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T20:12:27.000Z","msg":"我知道係有唔同嘅譯名，<br />\n習得性失助、無助學習、習得無助，etc. <br />\n<br />\n但我讀書嘅時候聽嘅係學習無助，<br />\n所以要我揀譯名，我會選擇用學習無助。<br />\n<br />\n但譯名並非最重點，<br />\n眼見呢個理論同香港現況有關係，<br />\n故此我分享。<br />\n<br />\n我對呢個理論亦稱不上熟悉，<br />\n如果有人有更多補充，我極級歡迎。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T20:27:47.000Z","msg":"因為唔熟悉所以咪用錯名<br />\n<br />\n唔係有無唔同譯法既問題<br />\n而係概念錯誤<br />\n<br />\n學習無助永遠只能夠係學習如何去變成無助既動賓結構<br />\n<br />\n唔可以變成單獨名詞<br />\n<br />\n要變名詞必須要將佢名詞化黎做形容詞，例如<br />\n學習無助感<br />\n<br />\n而且一早有人講過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xeHBBbP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxeHBBbP.png&h=e77e94a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想出文扮野前唔該爬下文先<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講你係台灣人呀"},{"pid":"43406a0590fdbae1a62b65fb23fc66dab7555841","tid":1191221,"uid":125597,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ad3b98ee67d4e6f60dea39a8c024fb5d7f636409","tid":1191221,"uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1aa34b3b10247e1b7840f8bbf1e9d2c0befc0334","tid":1191221,"uid":125597,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6debf9f704b664ed85e84c1f085ffc3a4e0462ee","tid":1191221,"uid":389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T19:59:08.000Z","msg":"學習無助乜Term黎？<br />\n<br />\nLearned指經學習的<br />\n<br />\n香港一向叫習得性無助，或者習得無助"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T20:12:27.000Z","msg":"我知道係有唔同嘅譯名，<br />\n習得性失助、無助學習、習得無助，etc. <br />\n<br />\n但我讀書嘅時候聽嘅係學習無助，<br />\n所以要我揀譯名，我會選擇用學習無助。<br />\n<br />\n但譯名並非最重點，<br />\n眼見呢個理論同香港現況有關係，<br />\n故此我分享。<br />\n<br />\n我對呢個理論亦稱不上熟悉，<br />\n如果有人有更多補充，我極級歡迎。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T20:27:47.000Z","msg":"因為唔熟悉所以咪用錯名<br />\n<br />\n唔係有無唔同譯法既問題<br />\n而係概念錯誤<br />\n<br />\n學習無助永遠只能夠係學習如何去變成無助既動賓結構<br />\n<br />\n唔可以變成單獨名詞<br />\n<br />\n要變名詞必須要將佢名詞化黎做形容詞，例如<br />\n學習無助感<br />\n<br />\n而且一早有人講過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xeHBBbP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxeHBBbP.png&h=e77e94a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想出文扮野前唔該爬下文先<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講你係台灣人呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T20:57:29.000Z","msg":"同一樣食物，有人叫竹輪，有人叫獅子狗，<br />\n關鍵在於呢個人第一次去了解呢樣事物嘅時候係聽咩名。<br />\n<br />\n你我學習同一理念時，<br />\n你聽到嘅或許係習得無助，<br />\n而我導師講嘅係學習無助，<br />\n我認為無分對錯，只係我讀書時期接觸到嘅名就係學習無助。<br />\n<br />\n我一開始亦有講，學習無助，又稱習得無助，Learned Helplessness。<br />\n如果『學習無助』呢個名令你不快，就請你選擇一個自己舒服的譯名吧。<br />\n<br />\n而且我再強調，眼見呢個理論同香港現況有關係，<br />\n故此我分享。<br />\n<br />\n我理解嘅連登，<br />\n亦唔係一個開post分享理念就等於扮嘢、提及之前有人提及過嘅理論就等於係台灣人嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n恕我未能理解係邊個位令你覺得我扮嘢，<br />\n亦恕我未能理解呢一切同台灣人之間嘅關係。<br />\n<br />\n但多謝你嘅關注，結果令呢個post有機會比更多人見到。"},{"pid":"f3b1d2d3feb9565035b5c6eea5d7585938aa8c2d","tid":1191221,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T21:37:25.000Z","msg":"[img]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇，GOOGLE完得呢個人講︰</span></span>[/img]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/08/053638_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2F053638_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg&h=aae945f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/08/053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2F053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg&h=42fed551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/08/053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2F053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg&h=42fed551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/08/053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2F053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg&h=42fed551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/08/053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2F053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg&h=42fed551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/08/053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2F053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg&h=42fed551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/08/053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2F053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg&h=42fed551&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"785b25902c6d072367abf185b584672dca91d8cd","tid":1191221,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T21:44:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4a382b83f0c99b8a7e58e5572c3ac99d4ee3f89","tid":1191221,"uid":125597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f3b1d2d3feb9565035b5c6eea5d7585938aa8c2d","tid":1191221,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T21:37:25.000Z","msg":"[img]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇，GOOGLE完得呢個人講︰</span></span>[/img]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/08/053638_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2F053638_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg&h=aae945f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/08/053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2F053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg&h=42fed551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/08/053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2F053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg&h=42fed551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/08/053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2F053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg&h=42fed551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/08/053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2F053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg&h=42fed551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/08/053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2F053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg&h=42fed551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/08/053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2F053639_e2bc7766fa807276d49f57aeded7175a.jpg&h=42fed551&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:22:19.000Z","msg":"唔理你動機係咩，<br />\n與樓上同一原理，<br />\n多謝你嘅注意力同埋宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cc4faa2f110140e12c4784aaf9b33e9d47dff1","tid":1191221,"uid":125597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"785b25902c6d072367abf185b584672dca91d8cd","tid":1191221,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T21:44:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:28:47.000Z","msg":"極簡主義都可以係一套價值，<br />\n如果覺得呢套就係自己相信嘅價值，<br />\n我會支持你用自己嘅力量捍衛呢套價值 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f918c8dedaea3464b9ee91f58ac7fe6c9b9d30","tid":1191221,"uid":29075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:55:36.000Z","msg":"推番上嚟"}]}